Translation and Localization Services









Neural Machine Translation: What It Is, And How It Impacts Translation Efficiency


A new and more accurate translation method, Neural MT, is changing the game for multilingual communication. View this webinar to understand how Lionbridge is increasing translation and localization efficiency—so you can focus on communicating with customers faster.


View Webinar









Engaging and supporting your customers, suppliers, and employees across all languages is a huge undertaking. Offload translation and localization tasks with high-quality, efficient solutions—and focus on your critical business initiatives.






Enterprise localization services and solutions
Whether you need to reach consumers worldwide, communicate internally with a global workforce, or collaborate with international partners, translation and localization services are a critical element of your strategy. But the translation process can be nuanced and labor intensive.
If you’re looking for a fully outsourced solution, use onDemand Translation  for accurate, culturally-relevant translations. A self-service, cloud-based delivery model, onDemand saves you time and money without sacrificing quality or customer service.
Or, if your organization has the resources to oversee the translation and localization process directly, use our suite of managed language services for a customized, hands-on approach.
Either way, working with Lionbridge can be a smart solution. Our efficiencies of scale will keep costs in check. We have the global presence, technology, and language and cultural expertise to help you reach, engage, and support customers around the world.












“I have a software update that needs to be launched in eight languages across 10 different regions.”
Software Localization


“I'm hosting a global conference where attendees speak several languages… but the presenter speaks only English.”
Interpretation Services


“I'm working with a new translation vendor and need to make sure that their translations are accurate and on brand.”
Language Quality Assurance












					Website Translation Services
				


				Get high-quality translation and localization solutions for all types of digital content.
			









					Translation Services
				


				Translate your content into more than 350 languages, ensuring the concepts remain intact to convey your message in a new market.
			









					App Localization
				


				From development through support, ensure your app works in multiple cultural contexts.
			









					Interpretation Services
				


				From live meetings to video conferences to telephonic service centers, get accurate interpretation in more than 350 languages.
			









					Language Quality Assurance
				


				Assess the quality of your localized content with Language Quality Services, an independent auditor of language services.
			









					Real-Time Translation
				


				Our real-time translation solution handles the specific demands that traditional professional translation services aren't able to.
			









					Software Localization
				


				From translation to localization to global technical requirements, adapt your software for multiple global markets.
			









					Technical Translation
				


				Translate your highly technical content with speed, efficiency, and accuracy.
			



 





