Lionbridge Technologies, Inc. is the world's largest provider of localization solutions.[1] Formed in 1996, the company offers a range of services.[clarification needed][2][3] Based in Waltham, Massachusetts, Lionbridge employs 6,000 people in 160 countries.[4]



